  "short_description": "This is a refreshing survival game of shooting and slashing that uniquely combines long-distance sniping, directional rhythm fitness, equipment matching, and battlefield support gameplay. It is perfect for players who enjoy exciting battles, violent killing, and satisfying decompression.",
