  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many years after the outbreak, survivors face another crisis caused by the evolution of infected persons. In order to return to the cities and clear the increasingly dangerous infected persons, the new government decides to adopt survival selection to select outstanding warriors and form combat troops with these warriors as the center. Any survivors aged 18 or over can participate in the selection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be able to choose to control 5 different characters and complete a 30-day survival exam in a small city. The base behind you can only provide limited support. You need to constantly strengthen yourself, make reasonable choices of treasures to complete the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you will experience exciting sword slashes, satisfying gunshots, the joy of headshots, intense battlefield support, and interesting directional key rhythm attacks. Let's do it together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Battlefield Support◆<br>Call for battlefield support and trigger them at the right time to solve the problems you encounter and make combat more exciting (will continue to increase with game updates).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/8ad7d7fdcafb659eb1d108c9a35eb41b.poster.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/8ad7d7fdcafb659eb1d108c9a35eb41b.webm?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/8ad7d7fdcafb659eb1d108c9a35eb41b.mp4?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Joyful Fitness◆<br>Quickly press the direction keys correctly and hit perfectly to improve your various important attributes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/dd02b4de54a5e8b239141a73475e498f.poster.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/dd02b4de54a5e8b239141a73475e498f.webm?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/dd02b4de54a5e8b239141a73475e498f.mp4?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ Clothing Battle Damage ◆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five characters in the game have detailed clothing battle damage designs. Each character's clothing has up to 10 stages of battle damage effects, bringing you a unique experience on your challenge journey. Please note that if you focus too much on the tattered clothes, it could lead to a tragedy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/7c6059cdd4992dfa04e29dc01bece212.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/aab1019bc478fc1259f614d242c2ba8b.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/ec8d273d90d725cabbb39f13eb4a86dc.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/d25030194bb685a66846dee827c6e91b.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/01130bf4b45dc5b762c0b35cd3f80910.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/703af337080e8f6988d5aec131ef8d82.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Sniping to Earn◆<br>Earn enough points by challenging long-range sniping targets to make the battlefield richer and more chaotic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/373d1dfb0c077c691d06d12ac7d9ab00.poster.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/373d1dfb0c077c691d06d12ac7d9ab00.webm?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/373d1dfb0c077c691d06d12ac7d9ab00.mp4?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Accessory Customization◆<br>Customize your equipment with reasonable combinations to better cope with enemies and special situations you encounter on that day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/e94b535772d59a22625acee03ab9704d.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a personally developed game. I can't compare it to many large-scale games, but I hope everyone can feel the novelty and joy in my game. I am very open to player feedback to make the game more enjoyable.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many years after the outbreak, survivors face another crisis caused by the evolution of infected persons. In order to return to the cities and clear the increasingly dangerous infected persons, the new government decides to adopt survival selection to select outstanding warriors and form combat troops with these warriors as the center. Any survivors aged 18 or over can participate in the selection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will be able to choose to control 5 different characters and complete a 30-day survival exam in a small city. The base behind you can only provide limited support. You need to constantly strengthen yourself, make reasonable choices of treasures to complete the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you will experience exciting sword slashes, satisfying gunshots, the joy of headshots, intense battlefield support, and interesting directional key rhythm attacks. Let's do it together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Battlefield Support◆<br>Call for battlefield support and trigger them at the right time to solve the problems you encounter and make combat more exciting (will continue to increase with game updates).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/8ad7d7fdcafb659eb1d108c9a35eb41b.poster.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/8ad7d7fdcafb659eb1d108c9a35eb41b.webm?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/8ad7d7fdcafb659eb1d108c9a35eb41b.mp4?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Joyful Fitness◆<br>Quickly press the direction keys correctly and hit perfectly to improve your various important attributes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/dd02b4de54a5e8b239141a73475e498f.poster.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/dd02b4de54a5e8b239141a73475e498f.webm?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/dd02b4de54a5e8b239141a73475e498f.mp4?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆ Clothing Battle Damage ◆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five characters in the game have detailed clothing battle damage designs. Each character's clothing has up to 10 stages of battle damage effects, bringing you a unique experience on your challenge journey. Please note that if you focus too much on the tattered clothes, it could lead to a tragedy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/7c6059cdd4992dfa04e29dc01bece212.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/aab1019bc478fc1259f614d242c2ba8b.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/ec8d273d90d725cabbb39f13eb4a86dc.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/d25030194bb685a66846dee827c6e91b.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/01130bf4b45dc5b762c0b35cd3f80910.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/703af337080e8f6988d5aec131ef8d82.avif?t=1738769317\" width=150 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Sniping to Earn◆<br>Earn enough points by challenging long-range sniping targets to make the battlefield richer and more chaotic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/373d1dfb0c077c691d06d12ac7d9ab00.poster.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/373d1dfb0c077c691d06d12ac7d9ab00.webm?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/373d1dfb0c077c691d06d12ac7d9ab00.mp4?t=1738769317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Accessory Customization◆<br>Customize your equipment with reasonable combinations to better cope with enemies and special situations you encounter on that day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3332670/extras/e94b535772d59a22625acee03ab9704d.avif?t=1738769317\" width=568 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a personally developed game. I can't compare it to many large-scale games, but I hope everyone can feel the novelty and joy in my game. I am very open to player feedback to make the game more enjoyable.</p>",
